<title>ạlqlb fqlbk mʿbdh</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ạlqlb fqlbk mʿbdh .. ạlrwḥ frwḥy tʿbdh
 ạlḥsn ạ̉mạm jmạlk lạ .. mkạn lrạ̉sh ysndh)2
 1- (yswʿ ạlfạdy ḥbyb ạlqlb .. fqlby ybạt ymjdh)2
 (bḥbh tsmw wtʿlw ḥyạty .. mdy̱ ạlạ̉yạm tw̉kdh)2
 2- (yswʿ yạ mạt bdylaⁿạ lmwty .. fkyf lʿqly yfṭnh)2
 (ky ạ̉ḥyạ ạ̉mạly wạ̉zhr ʿmry .. fbyn ḍlwʿy mwṭnh)2
 3- (nẓrt ʿyny gẖzyr dmạk .. fjỷt ljrḥk ạ̉ltẖmh)2
 (sẖfyt lrwḥy sẖfyt jrwḥy .. ạ̉ʿbdaⁿạ mtẖly tkrmh)2
 4- (qd jạl bkẖạṭry ywm lqạk .. mty̱ ạ̉lqạk fy ạlsḥb)2
 (ytm ạlwʿd wybdw snạk .. kmạ qd jạʾnạ fy ạlktb)2</lyrics>
</song>